narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Standard higher-level language course. L3 will prepare you pretty well, but still challenging.
Take it with Prof. Alexandrov!! She is FANTASTIC--she cares so much about her students, and she makes it a pleasure to come to class every day.
Great class. I would recommend it because it actually makes you learn without doing that much work.
Yes, it's a great course. You learn a ton and it's fun.

I would absolutely recommend this class. It's a small step up from L3, and it is very doable. There are a couple more presentations and in-class activities in L4 as compared to L3, but they aren't too hard by any means. We also read a novel at the end of the class, which helps to make use of all the vocab and grammar learned throughout the year.
